LICENSING OVERVIEW

This repository contains components under different licenses. No single
license applies to the entire repository.

1. Application code
   Files: index.html, app.js
   License: MIT License
   Full text: LICENSES/MIT.txt

2. Compiled silhouette dataset
   File: data/countries.js
   License: GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 or later
   Full texts: LICENSES/LGPL-3.0.txt and LICENSES/GPL-3.0.txt

3. Natural Earth source material
   Status: Public domain
   Details: THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md

The LGPL-covered dataset is kept in a separate file from the MIT-covered
application code. Preserve this file, the license texts, and the notices when
redistributing the repository.
